en_83492_0	A suspect has been arrested in connection with stealing a diamond and gems from a house at Erawwala area in Pannipitiya.The suspect has been arrested at the Mount Lavinia Maliban Junction by the officers of the Mirihana Special Crimes Operations Unit.
en_83492_1	Suspects have disguised as police officers, entered the house, assaulted the owner of the house and stolen gems and the diamond.
en_83492_2	A foreigner who had arrived to purchase the diamond was abducted.
en_83492_3	Police said the suspect is known as Thusitha Maduranga alias Matara Malli and he is a resident of Matara.
